name: FloatED-MOON (16) Free
description:
Hello, my name is Edmoon Holeworld
Humans usually called me The Moon.
Being simple is a bliss.
Do not have a so stylish life but happy.
Do not have any fancy car but moving forward.
Do not have many friends but loyal family.
For me, maybe, being not controlled by the other's expectation are the first step to achieve that simple things, and that's not simple.
